t was nice.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V2Np3GE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mx6wHCG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OS5N2nD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JEHltcY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ucrmxgi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rUm8g03.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HfeI5Kh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tR9L9GJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HhsuIDE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w3TYoLC.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Xi7Vt5i.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tq4VcSq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UlaGtTB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UqgNruO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This corgi is my spirit animal today coz I have next week off from work, wheee! I'll probably spend most of it on here, making too many posts, but who cares, I have the week off!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/fpItiho</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ParallelParkingInABurka]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Dump, pox edition</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Lt4oj5t</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3SJ19wR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After two years of making good choices</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LjPivFS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Masking, distancing,  avoiding crowded places</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XJsSlmw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The pox has hit my house... the kids missed the last fun days of school</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xyMFYWU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Spouse and I had to take days off work.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mQEhzEy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We're all vaccinated and boosted as appropriate</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uNw1Q2D.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But it's still hitting hard.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/upFDWZP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Thankfully the youngest is starting to perk up, so that means it must come to an end.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GKxlehn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>All of that anxiety any fear had dimmed until the positive tests came back.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/31Tbv41.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I felt the original fear again, from the early days,  what if one of us has a really bad case?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/durSglZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>All I can do is keep everyone hydrated, resting, taking vitamins.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3Txr0Uo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We're re-watching Stranger Things before the new season drops. It's a good distraction from the coughing.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7Dd2efS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We have friends and family, food and supplies, and flexible virtual jobs.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Va4FUop.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Considering all of that I guess getting the pox now is best case scenario, rather than in the beginning with no vaccine and hospitals full.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5TuM3s6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We'll stay home and quietly quarantine, like so many other families.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/568X6Kc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I just kind of wanted to call into the void a bit.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OPMZA3D.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hopefully this means we'll be extra immune for the next few months.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dvqdJTW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LPGjcVR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7U1Nffb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HZ2HVRW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5S6Nweb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jp2uqMB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2tzWI0F.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/opzugOG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O1EPICb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qF0FmYb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rcc4Fhj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dGBCoqR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GiAOpXj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The dog is, of course, delighted that we're all home and being lazy together. Thanks to anyone who read my random musings, may your homes be healthy.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Lt4oj5t</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mynameisminerva]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Using a jetpack to climb a mountain</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SVacI7D</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EqcxM9C.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pilot, a paramedic named Jamie Walsh, had only six days of training before he flew the suit up Helvellyn, the third highest peak in the UK. This impressive feat also demonstrates that the suit can be used in conditions a helicopter wouldn’t be able to fly in.

Jamie was able to fly to the summit of Helvellyn in just 3.5 minutes compared to the current response time of 1 hour and 15 minutes. The program hopes to implement the Jet Suit Paramedic in summer 2022 to help those that get injured in the area.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SVacI7D</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ImpatientMoth]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Who else remembers the epic battle? It continues again tomorrow!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ZTYmFcq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/F34KM35.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Who else remembers this and how it just took off?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h79iKwM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Last year's winner - Josh</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zAMVDsf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The most epic noodle-battle in history!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PAjfWej.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Rock-Paper-Scissors battle to determine who the true Josh Swain is!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DM5Uzsg.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.thejoshfight.com/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ZTYmFcq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[wazeewa]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Unionize all the things!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WhXjg69</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tckk6j0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WhXjg69</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PiercedViking]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>So proud!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ZFXCCvs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="htt