DATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5YzPG9J.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zgzXIu8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/patriottakes/status/1527315817586900993</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/17nzjbh.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"Du Mez tells Michel Martin she believes the Christian right is undermining democracy and fracturing the country."

Full Segment:  https://youtu.be/whV8heFHXoQ</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/sd1Xfiy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[springelmogizmo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What an as$hole lol</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PETqmCT</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/c1lhV5i.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PETqmCT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[trustfallaccident]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Let’s build a faun! Making hooves for fearne Calloway (critical role cosplay)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8ynvbfb</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xttkjlo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Started with a base boot that was heel-less. I took the laces off and glued the sides down to the tongue of the shoe. Then I covered the front “heel” with worbla for structure, and then covered that with foam clay. Sculpted the foam clay into a hoof shape, then went over it with 2 layers of wood glue.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/l3mQON8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Once the hooves were dry, I Painted them green, put opaque tights over the boots and glued them down, and added a fur trim to the front to hide the seam. The tights were painted with VERY watered down acrylic paint!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AmYn48o.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Better view of the legs! Excuse the mess that is my workshop haha! I Added green freckles to the top of the tights bc I thought it would be cute (and it is)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gYDUcyl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Lastly I added on moss, little mushrooms, and some vines to go up the calves! I may add fur pants to this later, but for now I’m super happy with it!!

